  "title": "M&E Techinician (Tuas/BMS system/HVAC) Ref: JY",
  "description": "<h2>Key Responsibilities</h2><ul><li><p>Perform preventive maintenance and minor repairs for HVAC, electrical, plumbing, lighting, fire protection, and building systems.</p></li><li><p>Troubleshoot equipment issues and respond promptly to alarms, power failures, and M&E breakdowns.</p></li><li><p>Monitor BMS alerts and record operating readings and maintenance activities.</p></li><li><p>Ensure compliance with safety regulations and internal SOPs; maintain logs and documentation.</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with contractors and support shutdowns, renovations, and new installations.</p></li><li><p>Provide emergency and standby support, including participation in shift or 24/7 duty rosters as required.</p></li></ul><h2>Qualifications & Requirements</h2><ul><li><p>ITE, Higher ITE, or Diploma in Mechanical, Electrical, or Building Services Engineering (or related field).</p></li><li><p>Minimum 2 years of experience in building maintenance or facilities management.</p></li><li><p>Hands-on experience with HVAC, electrical, or plumbing systems preferred.</p></li><li><p>Basic knowledge of M&E drawings, schematics, and maintenance systems (CMMS is an advantage).</p></li><li><p>Physically fit and willing to work shifts, weekends, after-hours, or in confined spaces.</p></li><li><p>Licensed Electrical Worker (LEW) certification is a plus.<br /></p><p><em><strong>Yee Jie Ling Jaslin (R1440114)</strong></em><br /><em><strong>Business Edge Personnel Services Pte Ltd (96C4864)</strong></em></p><p></p></li></ul>",
